transfer.description: Transfers `wad` amount of tokens to `dst` address.

transferFrom.description: Transfers `wad` amount of tokens from `src` address to `dst` address.

move.description: Moves `wad` amount of tokens from `src` address to `dst` address.

pull.description: Pulls `wad` amount of tokens from `usr` address.

push.description: Pushes `wad` amount of tokens to `usr` address.

constructor.description: Initializes the contract with the given chain ID.

DOMAIN_SEPARATOR.description: Returns the domain separator used for EIP-712.

PERMIT_TYPEHASH.description: Returns the typehash for the permit function.

allowance.description: Returns the amount of tokens that `src` address is allowed to spend on behalf of `guy` address.

approve.description: Approves `usr` address to spend `wad` amount of tokens.

burn.description: Burns `wad` amount of tokens from `usr` address.

decimals.description: Returns the number of decimals used by the token.

mint.description: Mints `wad` amount of tokens to `usr` address.

name.description: Returns the name of the token.

permit.description: Sets the allowance of `spender` for `holder` address with a permit signature.

rely.description: Adds `guy` address to the list of allowed addresses.

symbol.description: Returns the symbol of the token.

totalSupply.description: Returns the total supply of the token.

version.description: Returns the version of the contract.

Approval.description: Emitted when `src` address approves `guy` address to spend `wad` amount of tokens.

LogNote.description: Emitted when a note is logged.

Transfer.description: Emitted when `src` address transfers `wad` amount of tokens to `dst` address.
